Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:25.05,標題,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「收到恐嚇信的日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:40.50,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:50.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說墨須小姐  為什麼要約在女僕咖啡廳見面?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我早就想來一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼了?  Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:03.02,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,請您決定點什麼之後再叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:04.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來兩杯女僕咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天不用執班 可以好好‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,放鬆下! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然跟墨須小姐約會 是出軌 是出軌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還不能確定‧‧‧但
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:23.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,無論如何 不確認的話就無法斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:26.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可是我們這副身體在店內是藏不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果有什麼可以變裝的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:31.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那種裝備我們沒準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:35.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇的話可以變裝不如說是變身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:39.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是便宜的即溶咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 這種話妳要小聲點‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我這就為主人們端上飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們店裡有那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,誰知道‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在 您說的是哪位呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 不‧‧‧抱歉 我認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊呀 Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛無法直立站著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是 因為她很飄然的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家不是都這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:14.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:16.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,噓~! 梅洛 暴露了暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之暫時還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:26.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有蘇能變身的話  那就讓蘇來變身就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.40,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,用三點支撐得以直立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.40,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,但不能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼梅洛 快去確認Darling 是不是真的出軌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂 你幹什‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦啦~非常抱歉 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.64,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說梅洛 別玩女僕遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~不是 這是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被迫和相愛的人分開 淪落成女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原貴族千金的妄想設定中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好了啦! 快繼續當間蝶 悲戀中毒者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,悲戀中毒‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.30,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不用說的那麼過份‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:04.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之妳要好好盯著Darling向我們彙報情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:08.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我們接下來要去哪裡‧‧‧約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:10.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,唉!  真的是約會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.57,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,你有什麼推薦場所嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 不對  說不定是墨須小姐強邀的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.06,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,盡可能是沒什麼人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爺的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總感覺有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,似乎沒有不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你要負起領導責任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.40,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米‧‧‧米亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇~蘇小姐 妳在做什‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,汗‧‧‧汗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:38.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說~說起來‧‧‧蘇小姐水份不足時就會尋求水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:45.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,發出聲音會被老爺發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:45.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我明明已經沒有出汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,糟‧‧‧糟糕了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是您的發票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們走吧 Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~  好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請您慢走 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如不介意請看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,正在發售的新遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是角色扮演派對還是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:24.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大概是新遊戲的活動吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說Darling君 稍微逛一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我很擅長玩夾娃娃機的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有手也有胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,認錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好危險~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,似乎沒被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:49.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過帕皮有了手跟後 違和感好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐真會玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都說我很擅長了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們去安靜一點的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,電話電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,電話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇 不行 拿出來 拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼樣? 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要快點打電話才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇 下面 下面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,電話掉在下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇~蘇 太下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是屁股那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再肚臍下面‧‧‧附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在往上一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要快點打電話才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我打電話問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍微有點失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在遊戲中心花錢不能報帳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有點玩過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀~嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,終於安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我去買個冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我要咖啡口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳還真是喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思 我要香草跟咖啡口味‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感覺今天見到了人都好面熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝您的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,很好 沒暴露 沒暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,正巧有個沒人的販賣車 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.57,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~廁所廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡的話還能藏住下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可是胸部稍微有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇變了兩人份的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且還連在一起我們都沒辦法分開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就只剩我們兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.50,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,絕不容許失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.95,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但這樣就能直接確認Darling‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:24.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡嗎 有巨乳美少女的販賣車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:35.08,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,牛奶口味!  牛奶口味!  牛奶口味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們走 Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這次要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅 這裡稍微拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:45.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇和我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手 衣服是連一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳那麼用力拉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡是斯米亞 抵達潛入地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和預訂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,完全不像經歷空白期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拉克涅拉! 妳怎麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我一直跟著妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:29.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然大白天就去愛情旅館 墨須這傢伙真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.19,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒問題的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要‧‧‧要怎麼辦? 拉克涅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當然是去抓囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抓‧‧‧抓什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當然是去抓把柄啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,背著我們和協調員偷情這可是大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.20,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,淫蕩特工S女史的日常 場面刺激! 性擾處男奪其童貞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這會成為能敲詐的好素材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling才沒出軌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,肯定是有什麼緣由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.89,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他沒出軌 所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.71,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳那是什麼歪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之我要見Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:15.09,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,安靜一點 要被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:15.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好了 妳快點爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 拉克大姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們為什麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.87,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\frz15\fs70\c&H000000&\pos(634,552)}牛奶口味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.87,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H0000FF&\pos(656,645)}售完!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,瞞著妳們真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請好好說明!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:43.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 其實是 Darling君收到了這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦 是恐嚇信啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:58.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以 就想用約會遊戲來引出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看來我不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在此我有事想拜託大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:12.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在抓到犯人前大家能跟Darling君約會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好久沒跟Darling約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:32.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明該是這樣的 為什麼梅洛小姐也在?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:35.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明是難得一次的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請放心!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:44.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我的目標是成為老爺的情人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天是來協助米亞小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是~是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請交給我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:53.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我一定會讓你們兩個緊密結合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之協助就協助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:12:00.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說妳們兩個 這都是為了引出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們別忘‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.62,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,裝不認識 裝不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:13.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說起來她們說今天會安排個保鑣 不過那也太顯眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 梅洛努大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,平時承蒙您關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請您盡情享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有勞了 有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:21.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,用‧‧‧用臉通行?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道人魚是VIP待遇?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:32.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這位也是夠顯眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請使用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,任何地方都可以免費遊玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我先去淡水魚區域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請兩位慢慢逛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍後見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛這算是在幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.60,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\frz10\pos(466,202)\c&H000000&}全 免 費 票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.60,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\frz10\pos(520,320)\c&H000000&}美洛努‧羅雷萊   認可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她在這到底有多大的權力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快看 這兩隻魚在Kiss呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,求愛行動?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:43.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說不定牠們是戀人‧‧‧之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但牠們都是雄性喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為雄性搶地盤的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,很像Kiss的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以這種魚被稱作Kiss魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳為什麼要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不小心就幫你們解說起魚的知識了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼請看這隻海蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才不看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:20.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,順便一提海蛇分為爬蟲類和魚類兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎樣樣都好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:29.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛那傢伙居然用魚的知識來破壞氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.82,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常感謝大家今天的光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說梅洛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.29,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天本水族館有一位特別嘉賓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,差不多要開始了 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.53,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼有請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,各位大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然跑到那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:45.83,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天受美洛努大人的厚意 海豚表演變為人魚和海豚的共同表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.17,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,水族館還有人魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.58,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等 犯人說不定在監視我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這麼顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我會烘托氣氛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請你們進入良好的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:30.63,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼接下來是與海豚親密接觸的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦? 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.53,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,聽說有人魚參加演出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 Darling 光顧著看梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說好烘托氣氛結果卻搶走Darling 的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哇! 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦? 尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 我才該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:49.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:53.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來是他種族的小姐真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我稍微有點恍神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他種族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是蜥蜴人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡的空調開太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,體溫降低 頭有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:15.29,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,變溫性的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:11.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在冷氣附近感覺都會冬眠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:13.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,食物賣場的冷氣也很危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:19.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對了 這個可以溫暖身體 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝~謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說妳看起來好像很生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那~那是因為‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們去有太陽的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:35.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞和帥哥走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:37.53,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,這位客人 現在雖然是和海豚親近的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,追上他們比較好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.34,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是請您不要帶走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是又不能丟下Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.21,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,這位客人 這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還是這邊優先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.20,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,海豚要乾死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還豚也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被盯上的可不一定是Darling君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:48.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說不定對方盯上的是米亞或其他的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以才會恐嚇可能成為結婚對象的Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,也就是說‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,風稍微有些涼 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,穿上這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說那個男人還真是過份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,跟妳約會卻帶著別的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎 才沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:19.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為Darling很溫柔所以也會平等的照顧梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:23.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果他心中有妳的話怎會放著妳不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那都是梅洛的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她說要協助我 結果自己來搶風頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:33.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是 Darling是因為溫柔才無法放下梅洛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就是喜歡他這點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別再談男人的話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那種人類有什麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:44.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那種優柔寡斷不著邊際跟輕小說主角一樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想獨佔妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們都是爬蟲類肯定能相處的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果他要阻攔的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:57.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就把那個男人解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,能了解妳的人 只有同種類的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:06.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,確實拉米亞和蜥蜴人挺相近的 但‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蜥蜴人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才不是那種東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:14.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是爬蟲類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:17.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不對 是所有生物的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,擁有龍族血脈的王者血族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,龍人族的多拉珂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,龍人 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,D ?  難道就是他寄恐嚇信的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳只要順從我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我一直關注著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,終於‧‧‧能讓妳成為我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,救救我!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,救救我 Darling !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎‧‧‧怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:58.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你再對米亞做什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道打算就這麼撞過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不快點避開的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:09.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,槳 咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,船槳沒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:46.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快離開我老婆 你這人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:53.91,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,區區男人竟敢對身為生物頂點的我‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,誰是你老婆啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:19:59.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你濕成這樣可不只會感冒 可能會冬眠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好了 快把衣服脫了曬曬太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:12.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂! 你這手怎麼‧‧‧你要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,阿啦‧‧‧喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,女孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:26.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是 想找一個爬蟲類的‧‧‧朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳剛才不是說什麼老婆的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是該對朋友做的事情嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以說我討厭粗暴的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:33.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那妳為什麼要寄恐嚇信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,恐嚇信?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕對不會認同你的 混蛋~ ~ ~! !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧那個‧‧‧這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳轉過去一下 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:57.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,, Darling  這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我在店裡買的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個‧‧‧覺得很適合米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:14.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼說 沒有送給妳的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米~米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:19.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然Darling很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳沒有寄宿家庭的人陪同就擅自外出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今後如果再犯 你將接受嚴格的處分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好好記住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕不會放棄的!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:44.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,恐嚇信不是這孩子寄的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:23.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}帕皮 妳什麼想來這裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:26.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}哎 帕皮才沒有說過那種話
